![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1625596298833-GXZI8QSEI90UBD574VQQ/185.jpg)

It's been 11 years since we were first introduced to Natasha Romanoff in the MCU, as she stole our hearts and dropped our jaws in her Iron Man 2 debut. Since then she has fought alongside our heroes but has rarely had the spotlight herself. That ends today. With the Black Widow film quickly approaching, we decided to cover the story that introduces ANOTHER Black Widow in Yelena Belova who will also be introduced in live-action in the film. How does the OG Widow react to the new one? How does Natasha differ from comic to screen? All that and way more Widow in this jam-packed episode!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
